name: CIMERA DEVIL
description:
CIMERA DEVIL

It is an animal in Greek mythology, which legend has it said. 
He is the son of Echidna and Typhon. He is the elder brother of Cerberus.
CIMERA it has a stalwart body and is home to three kinds of beasts: a lion's head to chest, a goat's body, and a dragon or snake's buttocks.
Can spit fire like a dragon
